OL,3,CReport reveals Jersey's General
OL,4,CHospital could be 'an exemplar
OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,FJersey's General Hospital has "an
OL,8,Fopportunity to become an exemplar
OL,9,Fhospital", according to a new report
OL,10,Finto its Orthopaedic Services and
OL,11,Ftheatre efficiency.
OL,13,FThe review by Getting It Right First
OL,14,FTime (GIRFT) was carried out to
OL,15,Faddress long waiting times and ensure
OL,16,Fthe best outcome for patients.
OL,18,FIt describes the Hospital as currently
OL,19,Fdemonstrating "many examples of good
OL,20,Fpractice" but also recommends 36 areas
OL,21,Ffor improvement.
