OL,7,FThe review body says: "We saw
OL,8,Fexcellent facilities. This confirms
OL,9,Four view that Jersey General Hospital
OL,10,Fhas an opportunity to become an
OL,11,Fexemplary hospital, which will improve
OL,12,Fcare for all patients and encourage
OL,13,Fadditional private patients to use the
OL,14,Ffacilities."
