OL,7,FWe don't normally get to see this type
OL,8,Fof document, it's been released
OL,9,Faccording to the Health Minister,
OL,10,FDeputy Tom Binet, for transparency and
OL,11,Falso I think to make sure that the
OL,12,Fbuilding of the new hospital goes as
OL,13,Fsmoothly as possible.
OL,15,FMuch of it focuses on how to bring
OL,16,Fdown waiting times, which for
OL,17,Foutpatients in the Trauma and
OL,18,FOrthopaedics Unit currently stand at
OL,19,F10 weeks with over 1,100 people on the
OL,20,Flist to be seen.
