OL,7,FFor elective patients, those who
OL,8,Freceive non-urgent treatment, it is 17
OL,9,Fweeks with nearly 800 people waiting.
OL,11,FRecommendations suggest that the
OL,12,Fnumber of days theatres operate should
OL,13,Fincrease and a pool of standby
OL,14,Fpatients should be made available when
OL,15,Fcancellations happen.
