OL,4,CHospital could be 'an exemplar
OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,FThe review does reveal that the
OL,8,Fscanning equipment in the Radiology
OL,9,FDepartment is outdated and that the
OL,10,Fsoftware on the MRI scanner needs
OL,11,Frenewing as currently it is not
OL,12,Fpossible to screen for prostate cancer.
OL,14,FIt also recommends that there needs to
OL,15,Fbe a separate review of current
OL,16,Fequipment and upgrades where necessary.
OL,18,FThis is expensive tech though so some
OL,19,Fdecisions will be dependent on budgets.
