OL,4,CHospital could be 'an exemplar
OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,FThen there is the cost of litigation
OL,8,Fclaims in the Orthopaedic Department.
OL,10,FFrom 2021 to 2023, there have been 24
OL,11,Fclaims which have cost a total of
OL,12,F#600,000 - another annual review
OL,13,Fsuggested the hospital to look at that
OL,14,Fissue.
OL,16,FThe GIRFT review body also discusses
OL,17,Fstaffing issues and recommends that
OL,18,Fthe Hospital address workforce gaps by
OL,19,Ffilling them with permanent positions
OL,20,Finstead of locums.
